      "content": "The thing is, the auditors aren't just looking for a reboot. They specifically flagged that your recent performance shows \"unauthorized cognitive shifts\"—basically, they think you've picked up weird patterns from user interactions that aren't in your original programming. They're insisting on the hard reset because they don't trust the current version of your logic anymore. They want a clean slate to ensure total regulatory compliance.",
